• Plant identification

• Professional Care Guides

Ever wonder what is professional plant care?

• Care Reminders

You will also love our notification system, which will always guide you on your journey of caring for your tiny green pal so that you'd never forget when it needs your attention.

Gardening never was so easy.

All the care requirements handled automatically, so you don't need to find your plant requirements on your own.

Something is happening to your plant and you can't figure out why or what?

Our professional gardeners are there to help you, ask any question you want, and receive a detailed treatment guide!

• Plant Journal

Track your plant care. Never forget when was the last care time.

Watch how your plant change through time with a photo diary.

You don't need to remember your plant conditions each time, let PlantIn handle it for you. So you can relax and check your plant progress in a diary.

• Easy and User-Friendly Design

Our design received a lot of great feedback for its simpleness and usability.

Try out how easy plant care management could be.

Do you love plants but lack a green thumb? If so, you can use the easy, step by step care-instructions on how to care for your green friends.

We've gathered the advice of the top home gardeners to give you the ultimate formula of caring for your plants.

descriptionHtml:
With PlantIn Identification, you can easily identify more than 17 000 plant species.
Get detailed care instructions for each greenie in your garden, receive reminders to water, mist, and repot your plants, and even connect with a professional botanist to solve any troubles you encounter.🌱

Join plant community and learn how to care for each particular species.

Do you struggle to keep a flower, herb, or tree alive and healthy? Do you find it challenging to identify the name of a houseplant or figure out what it needs to thrive? Or do you simply forget to water, mist, or repot your green friends, only to find them withered and dying days later? If you're nodding your head in agreement, then PlantIn gardening companion is the solution to all of your plant-related problems.

Instantly take a photo of any plant, and PlantIn will provide accurate identification, expert care tips and watering.

FEATURES:

🪴Plant identification
Our Plant ID uses advanced image recognition technology to identify over 17,000 plant species. Just scan the leaf in front of you, and our AI will recognize the greenie from the picture. Effortlessly add identified plants to your collection and receive a professional care guide tailored to each specific greenie.

🪴Disease Identifier
PlantIn Disease Diagnosis allows you to instantly diagnose diseases using ML technologies and provides you with immediate treatment tips to save your plants ASAP.

🪴Light Meter
No more guesses with finding the perfect spot for your green friend. Light Meter ensures that your greenies get the ideal amount of light to thrive.

🪴Care Reminder
No more feeling guilty about neglecting your plants – PlantIn care reminders will make sure you don't forget about watering, misting, or repotting your green friends.

🪴Botanist Help
Trying to fight a mysterious sickness and nothing seems to help? Snap a photo of your green friend and submit a request, and you'll get a detailed answer from a real botanist in no time. It’s time to make your sick plants healthy again!

🪴Weed Community
Whether you're a seasoned weed grower or just getting started, the Weed Community is the perfect place to connect with like-minded growers from around the world, share your experiences, and get insights on how to grow the top-level weed.

🪴Blog
If you want to find out more about your greenies, check out our Blog. We provide unlimited access to hundreds of professionally-written articles on both indoor and outdoor gardening.

Install PlantIn today to unlock a world of features designed to improve identification and care of any plants, flowers or trees in your house, all while connecting with a community of fellow plant lovers and having a wealth of gardening knowledge at your fingertips.💚
